-- China Will `Soon' Publish Rules to Guide Steel Production, Securities Says
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-06-18T01:00:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-18/china-will-soon-publish-rules-to-guide-steel-production-securities-says.html

          
          
             China will “soon” announce
rules to guide production and operation in the steel industry,
the Shanghai Securities News  said , citing the Ministry of
Industry and Information Technology.  
 The rules will facilitate mergers, spur the removal of
obsolete capacity, and support bigger producers, the newspaper,
said today. The newspaper is affiliated with the state-run
Xinhua News Agency.  
 -- Xiao Yu . Editors:  Tan Hwee Ann ,  Andrew Hobbs .  
